description: The ever-acclaimed Chef Will & Chef David, with their collective 25+ years of experience, have unleashed their culinary talents onto the streets of Houston. Their unique offering of flavorful wild game options is causing the locals to rave about this big beastly bus. Their intensely tasty selection includes the hearty Lamb & Bison Cheesesteak on a toasted roll, yummy Duck Sliders, a crispy Fried Chicken Sandwich with sriracha, and so much more. name: On The Wild Side Catering
